title: 10X Your Income And Influence With A Top Shelf Podcast
itunes:title: 10X Your Income And Influence With A Top Shelf Podcast
description:
Become the authority in your market by implementing these steps and becoming a top shelf podcaster. I went from the ex-con turned underdog entrepreneur afterthought to my perfect clients lining up to get with me by launching my podcast.
 
Here’s my guide for top-shelf podcasting: https://www.podcastpenthouse.com/roadmaps
 
Learn more about Underdog Empowerment here: https://underdogempowerment.com/098
